<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>OpenTelemetry でオブザーバビリティをクラウドネイティブにする on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/</link><description>Recent content in OpenTelemetry でオブザーバビリティをクラウドネイティブにする on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>ja</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector Contrib のインストール</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/1-installation/1-confirmation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/1-installation/1-confirmation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="collector-が動作していることを確認する"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Collector が動作していることを確認する&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#collector-%e3%81%8c%e5%8b%95%e4%bd%9c%e3%81%97%e3%81%a6%e3%81%84%e3%82%8b%e3%81%93%e3%81%a8%e3%82%92%e7%a2%ba%e8%aa%8d%e3%81%99%e3%82%8b" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collector が動作しているはずです。&lt;code&gt;systemctl&lt;/code&gt; コマンドを使用して root として確認します。ステータス表示を終了するには &lt;code&gt;q&lt;/code&gt; を押してください。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector エクスポーター</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/5-exporters/1-otlphttp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/5-exporters/1-otlphttp/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="otlp-http-exporter"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;OTLP HTTP Exporter&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#otlp-http-exporter" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HTTP 経由で Splunk Observability Cloud にメトリクスを送信するには、&lt;strong&gt;otlphttp&lt;/strong&gt; エクスポーターを設定する必要があります。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;/etc/otelcol-contrib/config.yaml&lt;/code&gt; ファイルを編集して、&lt;strong&gt;otlphttp&lt;/strong&gt; エクスポーターを設定しましょう。以下の YAML を &lt;strong&gt;exporters&lt;/strong&gt; セクションの下に挿入してください。インデントはスペース2つ分にしてください。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector レシーバー</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/3-receivers/3-other-receivers/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/3-receivers/3-other-receivers/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="その他のレシーバー"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;その他のレシーバー&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#%e3%81%9d%e3%81%ae%e4%bb%96%e3%81%ae%e3%83%ac%e3%82%b7%e3%83%bc%e3%83%90%e3%83%bc" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;デフォルト設定には、&lt;strong&gt;otlp&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;opencensus&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;jaeger&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;zipkin&lt;/strong&gt; という他のレシーバーがあることに気づくでしょう。これらは他のソースからテレメトリデータを受信するために使用されます。このワークショップではこれらのレシーバーについては扱いませんので、そのままにしておいてください。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector Processors</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/4-processors/3-attributes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/4-processors/3-attributes/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="attributes-processor"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Attributes Processor&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#attributes-processor" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Attributes プロセッサーは、スパン、ログ、またはメトリクスの属性を変更します。このプロセッサーは、指定されたアクションに対して含めるか除外するかを決定するために、入力データのフィルタリングとマッチングもサポートしています。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector Service</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/6-service/5-otlphttp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/6-service/5-otlphttp/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="otlp-http-exporter"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;OTLP HTTP Exporter&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#otlp-http-exporter" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ワークショップの Exporters セクションで、Splunk Observability Cloud にメトリクスを送信するための &lt;code&gt;otlphttp&lt;/code&gt; エクスポーターを設定しました。次に、これを metrics パイプラインで有効にする必要があります。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector Development</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/1-project-setup/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/1-project-setup/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="project-setup"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Project Setup &lt;span class="badge badge--accent"&gt;&lt;span class="badge__icon"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#project-setup" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ninja&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="callout callout--note"&gt;&lt;span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z M14 2v6h6 M9 13h6 M9 17h6"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Note&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p&gt;このセクションを完了するまでの時間は、経験によって異なります。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;行き詰まった場合やインストラクターと一緒に進めたい場合は、&lt;a href="https://github.com/splunk/collector-workshop-example" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;こちら&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;svg class="link-ext" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="M7 17 17 7"/&gt;&lt;path d="M9 7h8v8"/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
に完全なソリューションがあります。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector 開発</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/3-component/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/3-component/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="コンポーネントレビュー"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;コンポーネントレビュー&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#%e3%82%b3%e3%83%b3%e3%83%9d%e3%83%bc%e3%83%8d%e3%83%b3%e3%83%88%e3%83%ac%e3%83%93%e3%83%a5%e3%83%bc" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jenkins からメトリクスを取得するために必要なコンポーネントの種類を振り返ります&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Extension"&gt;Extension&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Receiver"&gt;Receiver&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-2" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-2" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Processor"&gt;Processor&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-3" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-3" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Exporter"&gt;Exporter&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-4" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-4" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Connectors"&gt;Connectors&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs---home-runner-work-observability-workshop-observability-workshop-content-ja-ninja-workshops-foundations-3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops-1-opentelemetry-collector-8-develop-3-component-md-11-1--0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Extension"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Extension が解決するビジネスユースケースは以下の通りです&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OpenTelemetry Collector Development</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/5-business-logic/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ja/ninja-workshops/foundations/3-opentelemetry-collector-workshops/1-opentelemetry-collector/8-develop/5-business-logic/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="ビジネスロジックの構築"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;ビジネスロジックの構築&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#%e3%83%93%e3%82%b8%e3%83%8d%e3%82%b9%e3%83%ad%e3%82%b8%e3%83%83%e3%82%af%e3%81%ae%e6%a7%8b%e7%af%89" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;この時点では、現在何もしないカスタムコンポーネントがあるため、Jenkins からデータをキャプチャするために必要なロジックを追加する必要があります。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>